		- Delete existing book
		- Fetch Book
		- Fetch Books by Author
		- Fetch Books by Category

	- Author
		- Insert Author
		- Update author details
		- Delete author
		- Fetch author

	- User
		- Insert User
		- Update User
		- Delete User
		- Fetch User Details
		- Fetch All books issued to User


Flow :
    1. Creating Basic Api's
    2. Apply Validation
    3. Apply Exception Handling

